# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : owl:InverseFunctionalProperty

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

### Alice and Bob share the same passport number through an inverse-
### functional property -> they must be inferred identical.
:InverseFunctionalProperty_Alice owl:sameAs :InverseFunctionalProperty_Bob .
